---
// Pricing section component
---
<section id="pricing" class="bg-primary-soft py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Our Pricing</h3>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">We offer great prices, premium products and <span class="text-gradient">quality</span> service for your business.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-8 flex flex-col items-center">
        <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">$899<span class="text-lg font-normal">/mo</span></h3>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Corporate Plan</h4>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>AI Tools &amp; Appointment Booking</li>
          <li>2-Way SMS &amp; Call Tracking</li>
          <li>Review Management</li>
          <li>CRM &amp; Pipeline Mgmt</li>
          <li>Automated Campaigns</li>
          <li>24/7 Support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-primary-dark transition">Choose Plan</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-8 flex flex-col items-center">
        <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">$1099<span class="text-lg font-normal">/mo</span></h3>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Premium Plan</h4>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>AI Tools &amp; Appointment Booking</li>
          <li>2-Way SMS &amp; Call Tracking</li>
          <li>Review Management</li>
          <li>CRM &amp; Pipeline Mgmt</li>
          <li>Automated Campaigns</li>
          <li>24/7 Support</li>
          <li>Custom Integrated Website</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-primary-dark transition">Choose Plan</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Can I cancel my subscription?</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. You can cancel your plan at any time from your account dashboard—no contracts, no hidden fees.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How can I manage my account?</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600">All account settings, billing info, and user permissions can be updated from your Admin panel. You’re in full control.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Is my customer data and payment info secure?</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Yes—our platform is PCI-compliant and uses bank-grade encryption to keep your customer and payment data protected.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How long does it take to get set up?</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Most customers are fully onboarded within 1–3 days. We’ll walk you through every step and offer live setup support.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 